leading dog
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a dog used to go in front of a mob to control its speed and stop it breaking or stampeding (cf. lead v and n3.)
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
